Question: Are both the palm tree in front of the wall and the palm to the left of the flag brown?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n507959.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='wall')
IMAGE0=CROP_ABOVE(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='palm tree')
IMAGE1=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='palm tree')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE,question='What color is the palm tree in front of the wall?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE,question='What color is the palm to the left of the flag?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'brown' and {ANSWER1} == 'brown' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
